OL,7,FWatch Sam Blackledge's report as the
OL,8,Fdefence case concludes in the
OL,9,FChristine Rawle murder trial
OL,11,FA former council contractor who was
OL,12,Fallegedly stabbed to death by his wife
OL,13,Fthreatened and insulted a couple he
OL,14,Fwas working for, a court has heard.
OL,16,FHe spat at them, urinated on their
OL,17,Fdoorstep and warned them he would slit
OL,18,Ftheir throats, a jury was told today,
OL,19,FTuesday 19 March.
