OL,7,FMr Bowden told the court that Mr Rawle
OL,8,Falso insulted his wife.
OL,10,F"My wife is a doctor, she was on her
OL,11,Fcomputer and he made a sneering
OL,12,Fcomment that she was probably playing
OL,13,Fa computer game," he said.
OL,15,F"He arrived three times that week.
OL,16,FOnce I was on the phone complaining
OL,17,Fabout him, he tried to walk into our
OL,18,Fkitchen, I stopped him.
