OL,7,F"He said I was a very stupid person
OL,8,Fand he said 'I can get people round
OL,9,Fhere to sort you out'. He then said
OL,10,Fthat again and made a gesture to his
OL,11,Fthroat. That was aimed at my wife."
OL,13,FMr Bowden demonstrated the gesture to
OL,14,Fthe court, pulling his finger across
OL,15,Fhis throat.
OL,17,FThe court also heard from John
OL,18,FPriddle, who had been walking in woods
OL,19,Fnear the Rawles' home on the day Ian
OL,20,Fdied.
