OL,7,F"I couldn't work out exactly where it
OL,8,Fwas coming from or how far away it
OL,9,Fwas. I felt quite helpless, I felt
OL,10,Flike I should be helping.
OL,12,F"It seemed like there was something
OL,13,Fserious happening. Soon after that we
OL,14,Fsaw a helicopter and emergency
OL,15,Fvehicles."
OL,17,FChristine Rawle denies murder and the
OL,18,Ftrial continues.
